== 製作 ==
===發展===
2003年，監製[[羅倫佐·狄·波納馮杜拉|羅倫佐·狄·波納馮杜拉]]有意打造一部先進軍事科技的影片，[[孩之寶|孩之寶]]執行長{{link-en|布萊恩·高登納|Brian Goldner}}提出改編[[大英雄|特種部隊]]玩具模型的拍攝計畫<ref>{{cite news|author=Andria Cheng|title=Hasbro's chief transformer|work=[[MarketWatch|MarketWatch]]|date=2008-12-04|url=http://www.marketwatch.com/news/story/goldner-scripts-blockbuster-hasbros-chief/story.aspx?guid={978E3D48-FCD3-4ABC-BCF6-3C0242AC1622}|accessdate=2008-12-04}}</ref>。還身為[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]的執行長波納馮杜拉，與曾一起合作的高登納將此系列推上大螢幕，兩人花三個月時間展開故事企畫，挑選麥可·B·戈登作為編劇，他們欣賞戈登在《[[300壯士：斯巴達的逆襲|300壯士：斯巴達的逆襲]]》編劇天賦<ref>{{cite news | author=Michael Fleming | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117892462.html | title=Lorenzo drafts G.I. Joe | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2003-09-15 | accessdate= 2008-02-23}}</ref>。波納馮杜拉想要描述各個角色的背景故事，即角色們加入部隊的過去種種，以及增加新的角色雷克斯，成為公爵自我探索推展劇情的關鍵<ref name=stand>{{cite news | author=Stax | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/497/497708p1.html | title=Producer Talks ''G.I. Joe'' | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2004-03-10 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2012-02-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229171135/http://movies.ign.com/articles/497/497708p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。雷克斯的取名由孩之寶公司所創<ref>{{cite news | author=Stax | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/498/498953p1.html | title=Screenwriter Talks ''G.I. Joe'' | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2004-03-15 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2012-02-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206061752/http://movies.ign.com/articles/498/498953p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之前，監製{{link-en|唐·墨菲|Don Murphy}}對本片拍攝感到興趣，但正值[[伊拉克戰爭|伊拉克戰爭]]爆發，考慮到議題時局過於敏感，而選擇發展孩之寶另一知名玩具系列《[[變形金剛|變形金剛]]》<ref>{{cite news | author = Kellvin Chavez | title = On Set Interview: Producer Don Murphy On Transformers | work = Latino Review | date = 2007-02-21 | url = http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=1502 | accessdate = 2008-02-23 | archive-date = 2009-01-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090124174404/http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=1502 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。波納馮杜拉認為「不管［特種部隊］代表什麼，特別在電影裡也不論公爵出自於哪裡，這就是我想要全世界觀眾都能感受到。」<ref name=stand/>

2005年2月，請來同為波納馮杜拉監製電影《[[血盟兄弟|血盟兄弟]]》的編劇保羅·拉維特和大衛·艾略特翻修劇本<ref>{{cite news | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/584/584119p1.html | title=Exclusive: ''G.I. Joe'' Enlists New Writers | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2005-02-01 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2008-01-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110181130/http://movies.ign.com/articles/584/584119p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在新的劇本裡，角色雷克斯墮入偏門與卡通裡的眼鏡蛇指揮官作結合，與戴斯卓聯手成立一群超級部隊<ref>{{cite news|author=El Mayimbe|url=http://www.latinoreview.com/script-reviews/7|title=G.I. Joe by David Elliot and Paul Lovett, revised first draft dated September 16, 2005, 116 pages|work=Latino Review|date=2005-12-30|accessdate=2008-10-01|archive-date=2008-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914044513/http://www.latinoreview.com/script-reviews/7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年3月，{{link-en|史奇普·伍茲|Skip Woods}}再度翻修劇本，新增來自英國軍人角色艾利克·曼恩，監製解釋「不幸地，[[乔治·沃克·布什|布什]]總統讓我們在國際上的地位很難去宣傳這部電影「G.I. Joe」（意指美國大兵），而新增一個角色混雜其中是件挺有趣的事」<ref name=worst>{{cite news | author=George Roush | url=http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=1566 | title=Exclusive 1-1 With Lorenzo Di Bonaventura | work=Latino Review | date=2007-03-07 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2019-06-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609031137/http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=1566 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。影評家艾·梅伊比（El Mayimbe）揭露在伍茲的編劇版本，刪去眼睛蛇組織裡的隱匿於[[CIA|CIA]]特務雷恩，史嘉蕾與艾利克曼恩結婚，但仍對公爵有所好感，且男爵夫人亦身亡。蛇眼有張口說話，但在劇情裡聲帶是受損的，仍以姿體表達。梅伊比建議應由{{link-en|史都華·畢提|Stuart Beattie}}重寫劇本<ref>{{cite news | author = El Mayimbe | title = G.I. JOE by Skip Woods, First Draft, 121 pages | work = Latino Review | date = 2008-05-21 | url = http://www.latinoreview.com/scriptreview.php?id=62 | accessdate = 2008-02-26 | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125051433/http://www.latinoreview.com/scriptreview.php?id=62 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
影迷對於此版本的劇情提出負面評價反彈，波納馮杜拉承諾會立即重編「我期望這次我們將會呈現的更好給大眾。」<ref name=badskip>{{cite news | author=Scott Collura | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/796/796434p1.html | title=Exclusive: G.I. Joe Update | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2007-06-14 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2011-05-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522121056/http://movies.ign.com/articles/796/796434p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>他承認眼鏡蛇的橋段有些問題，在訪談裡同意「他們在［卡通裡的表現］或許是最愚蠢的邪惡組織。」<ref name=worst/>孩之寶保證他們絕對會把眼鏡蛇寫回劇本裡<ref>{{cite news | author=El Mayimbe | url=http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2376 | title=G.I. Joe Exclusive Update with Hasbro COO | work=Latino Review | date=2007-07-12 | accessdate=2008-02-23 | archive-date=2020-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728073005/http://www.latinoreview.com/news.php?id=2376 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年8月，[[史蒂芬·桑莫斯|史蒂芬·桑莫斯]]向[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]執行長{{link-en|布萊德·格雷|Brad Grey}}引薦自己來執導本片，以及製作部分布萊德·華盛頓說明構想近而錄用<ref name=sommers>{{cite news | author=Michael Fleming | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117970752.html | title=Stephen Sommers to direct 'G.I. Joe' | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2007-08-23 | accessdate=2008-02-22}}</ref>。導演桑莫在拜訪[[孩之寶|孩之寶]]位於[[羅德島州|羅德島州]]的總部後，激起將特種部隊拓展為全世界聯盟組織的想法。<ref>{{cite news | author=Borys Kit | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/peopleNews/idUSN2430477820070824 | title="G.I. Joe" accepts movie assignment | publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] | date=2007-08-24 | accessdate=2008-02-22 | archive-date=2020-12-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204153256/https://www.reuters.com/article/peopleNews/idUSN2430477820070824 | dead-url=no }}</ref>基於監製波納馮杜拉以及莫菲製作的《[[變形金剛_(2007年電影)|變形金剛]]》，賣座票房成為本片改編製作的一大動力<ref name=sommers/>。桑莫斯來執導本片部分原因在於，此電影概念上會聯想到[[詹姆士·龐德|詹姆士·龐德]]，並且表示劇情裡的水底大戰，是向007系列第四部電影《[[霹靂彈|霹靂彈]]》致敬<ref>{{cite news|author=Clark Collis|title='G.I. Joe' director denies making Sienna Miller wear rubber breasts|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2009-01-22|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/01/gi-joe-director.html|accessdate=2009-01-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124160518/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/01/gi-joe-director.html|archivedate=2009-01-24}}</ref>。史都華·畢提受邀來改編新的劇本<ref>{{cite news | author=Tatiana Siegel | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117971136.html | title=Stuart Beattie to report for 'G.I.' duty | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2007-08-30 | accessdate=2008-02-22 }}</ref>，特種部隊的原創者{{link-en|賴瑞·哈瑪|Larry Hama}}成為本片創意[[顧問|顧問]]。哈瑪協助改編支持者可能不喜歡的故事要素，使劇本更能貼近漫畫，讓漫畫迷們更喜歡新的劇本<ref>{{cite news|title=Exclusive Video Interview: G.I. Joe Movie Creative Consultant Larry Hama! |work=IESB |date=2008-02-17 |url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4328&Itemid=99 |accessdate=2008-02-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218220634/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4328&Itemid=99 |archivedate=2008-02-18 }}</ref>。他說服編劇刪去電影結尾蛇眼說話的場景<ref>{{cite news|author=Brian Jacks|title=Snake-Eyes To Stay Silent For ‘G.I. Joe’ Movie, Promises Film’s Producer|work=[[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog|date=2008-07-25|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/07/25/snake-eyes-to-stay-silent-for-gi-joe-movie-promises-films-producer/|accessdate=2008-07-25|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001033723/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/07/25/snake-eyes-to-stay-silent-for-gi-joe-movie-promises-films-producer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為趕在[[2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工|2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工]]前加緊腳步製作，[[約翰·李·漢考克|約翰·李·漢考克]]、{{link-en|布萊恩·考波曼|Brian Koppelman}}和{{link-en|大衛·李維恩|David Levien}}也一同參與編劇作業<ref>{{cite news | author = Borys Kit | title = Hollywood flips over WGA contract deadline | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2007-10-30 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ie25482ef248abb48e568c60b2e2d4220 | accessdate = 2008-02-23 | archive-date = 2008-05-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517081806/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ie25482ef248abb48e568c60b2e2d4220 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。戈登提到他的寫作靈感是源自於哈瑪的漫畫，並非卡通<ref>{{cite news | author = Larry Carroll, Brian Jacks | title = 'G.I. Joe' Executive Producer Reveals Details About The Flick ... And The Action Figures! | work = [[MTV|MTV]] | date = 2008-03-03 | url = http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1582608/story.jhtml | accessdate = 2008-10-13 | archive-date = 2010-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100427075916/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1582608/story.jhtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。桑莫斯表示他對本系列背景故事並不完全熟透，電影有可能會因罷工事件而進度落後<ref name=savage>{{cite news|url=http://gijoeclub.com/Sommers0209-intv2.cfm|title=Stephen Sommers interview|work=G.I. Joe Collectors Club|author=Brian Savage|accessdate=2009-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711092753/http://gijoeclub.com/Sommers0209-intv2.cfm|archive-date=2011-07-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

