== 發行 ==
電影於2009年7月31日在美國[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[安德鲁斯空军基地|安德魯斯空軍基地]]首次播映<ref name="waves">{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/03/business/fi-ct-gijoe3 |title=Paramount Pictures waves the flag for ''G.I. Joe'' |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |first=Claudia |last=Eller |first2=Ben |last2=Fritz |date=2009-08-03 |accessdate=2009-09-28 |page=1 |archive-date=2009-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091012070516/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/03/business/fi-ct-gijoe3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而首映式則在同年8月7日於[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]的[[中國戲院|中國戲院]]舉行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/movies/features/article_1494259.php/In-Pictures-Los-Angeles-Premiere-of-G-I-Joe-The-Rise-Of-Cobra |title=In Pictures: Los Angeles Premiere of ''G.I. Joe: The Rise Of Cobra'' |publisher=Monsters and Critics |date=2009-09-30 |accessdate=2016-12-17 |archive-date=2009-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090913121417/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/movies/features/article_1494259.php/In-Pictures-Los-Angeles-Premiere-of-G-I-Joe-The-Rise-Of-Cobra |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隔天，《特種部隊：眼鏡蛇的崛起》便在美國的4,007家劇院發行<ref name="opening">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2609&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: ''G.I. Joe'' Doesn't Roll Snake Eyes |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2009-08-10 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2009-09-28 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905193519/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2609&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，除此之外，電影還於35個海外市場上映<ref name="world">{{cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/world-surrenders-to-gi-joes-100m-box-office-breach/5004427.article |title=World surrenders to G.I. Joe's $100m box office breach |date=2009-08-10 |first=Jeremy |last=Kay |publisher=ScreenDaily |accessdate=2009-09-28 |archive-date=2014-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111210028/http://www.screendaily.com/news/world-surrenders-to-gi-joes-100m-box-office-breach/5004427.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《特種部隊：眼鏡蛇的崛起》收穫了褒貶不一的評價。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的159篇專業影評文章，其中55篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為35%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]4.6分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|title=G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra (2009)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gi_joe_the_rise_of_cobra/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2014-02-08|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211185929/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gi_joe_the_rise_of_cobra|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的25篇評論文章，其中6篇予以好評，12篇差評，7篇褒貶不一，平均分為32（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/gijoeriseofcobra |title=''G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra'' (2009): Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=''CNET Networks'' |accessdate=2009-08-13 |archive-date=2010-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211143906/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/gijoeriseofcobra |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
美國上映當週戲院廳數4007家，共創下五千四百七十萬[[美元|美元]]的票房佳績，且在全球各地進帳四千四百萬美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/10/movies/10arts-GIJOEISNO1AT_BRF.html?hpw|title=‘G.I. Joe’ Is No. 1 at the Box Office|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2009-08-10|accessdate=2009-08-11|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629034539/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/10/movies/10arts-GIJOEISNO1AT_BRF.html?hpw|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2009年8月12日，[[美國|美國]]電影票房總計七千一百八十萬美元，美國以外票房達六千一百四十萬美元，全球總計一億三千三百三十萬美元。

台灣方面，最終全台票房為新台幣1.32億元<ref name="appledaily32180148">{{cite news |author1=陳泓銘 |title=09台灣西片總票房 無敵《變形金剛》 續集吸5.7億稱霸 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20091223/32180148 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2009-12-23 |accessdate=2018-02-28 |archive-date=2018-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180224213059/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20091223/32180148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

